   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bring Clean Water to 15 Villages in Rural Gambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This campaign began as way to raise funds for the Gambia Lifewater Project and the work of its leader Jeremy Mak. He wound up doing a TON of well &amp; handpump repair in The Gambia, as well as other water projects wherever he found himself. (Colombia, Uganda etc.)  Jeremy has shifted his focus now, and this campaign is continuing w/ focus on Water Charity&apos;s many projects in The Gambia &amp; nearby regions. We continue to repair broken handpumps &amp; help with water issues in other ways there. Thank you!</narrative>
  </description>
